{
  "stem": "3605.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if you took it off, and he was noticed-- recognized by somebody-- right away, he would have been shot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was very worried when he heard from somebody that he's taking off the armband once he goes out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said, next time the [NON-ENGLISH] is going to send somebody to Piotrkow, I am going to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the beginning of 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a new law came out, whereby Jews couldn't travel, permit or no permit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was 30 kilometers away from our home, and he couldn't come home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he would have taken his life immediately in his hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had-- this was his home town, originally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- Piotrkow?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Piotrkow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, he-- he lived there in-- in-- in a rooming place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very-- a great hardship for our family to be separated from my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was kind of like a shining star in our family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A man that was-- [SPEAKING HEBREW], which means 'a man of joy and a man-- man of good deeds.' It-- it was just very hard not to see him and not to have a hope for him to come home.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That he-- and this was a law, that he couldn't come home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The law came out when he was there, and there was no-- you cannot-- you couldn't-- even the [NON-ENGLISH] could do nothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this was a general law, and nobody could break it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was very, very rough for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I mentioned, when the news came in from the underground, when our contact came, they decided that it is time to join-- to smuggle out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
